  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have any suggestions or bug reports, please join the Discord channel for discussion~!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/2926d79f8be6016cec2ec55b1b371774.avif?t=1764856876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/9c55e02620bbe2a02f82f92d751f2b52.avif?t=1764856876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Kitten Food Alley</i> is a casual management sim with the theme of petting cat. You can open various food shops and adjust food recipes, produce food by petting cat employees.  Unlock various tools to automate petting. Enjoy the stress relief of cyber cat petting!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: The game can be played for about 1.5 to 2.5 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b2c937ab03a90039409cd733ff381d6.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b2c937ab03a90039409cd733ff381d6.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b2c937ab03a90039409cd733ff381d6.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/7808d7b5eb6baf954d75c294867f6c4d.avif?t=1764856876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend cat coins to build a store to start a new day, petting cat employees to make delicious food, and get cat coins and love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/fc35b8358b0f4b493df89a3c8a67e02f.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/fc35b8358b0f4b493df89a3c8a67e02f.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/fc35b8358b0f4b493df89a3c8a67e02f.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect customer feedback and adjust food recipes to increase the store's customer visit rate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/8fc4783633faf18c8670417699d38591.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/8fc4783633faf18c8670417699d38591.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/8fc4783633faf18c8670417699d38591.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock useful tools with love to better achieve the goal. Once the goal is achieved, you can enter the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b26755751642910a150137c70a548d1.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=298 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b26755751642910a150137c70a548d1.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b26755751642910a150137c70a548d1.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f27f9d1d7b4c822bd410dd81f52bce6.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=298 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f27f9d1d7b4c822bd410dd81f52bce6.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f27f9d1d7b4c822bd410dd81f52bce6.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f9c73f65b5f8bf110b681ead9672a45.avif?t=1764856876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When petting a cat, there will be lovely graphic animations and sound feedback.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 12 different types of stores in the game, such as popsicle stores, dumpling stores, and jianbing guozi stores.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a total of 5 levels. After unlocking each level, new items can be obtained. Reasonable use of various items can increase the efficiency of petting cats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reasonably arrange props to let the cat store operate on its own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple goals that can be accomplished without too much thought.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What <i>Kitten Food Alley</i> does <strong>not </strong>offer:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Customizable content.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Complex business strategy.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Task goals with pressure or time limits.</span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/9c55e02620bbe2a02f82f92d751f2b52.avif?t=1764856876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Kitten Food Alley</i> is a casual management sim with the theme of petting cat. You can open various food shops and adjust food recipes, produce food by petting cat employees.  Unlock various tools to automate petting. Enjoy the stress relief of cyber cat petting!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note: The game can be played for about 1.5 to 2.5 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b2c937ab03a90039409cd733ff381d6.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b2c937ab03a90039409cd733ff381d6.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b2c937ab03a90039409cd733ff381d6.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/7808d7b5eb6baf954d75c294867f6c4d.avif?t=1764856876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend cat coins to build a store to start a new day, petting cat employees to make delicious food, and get cat coins and love.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/fc35b8358b0f4b493df89a3c8a67e02f.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/fc35b8358b0f4b493df89a3c8a67e02f.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/fc35b8358b0f4b493df89a3c8a67e02f.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect customer feedback and adjust food recipes to increase the store's customer visit rate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/8fc4783633faf18c8670417699d38591.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/8fc4783633faf18c8670417699d38591.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/8fc4783633faf18c8670417699d38591.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock useful tools with love to better achieve the goal. Once the goal is achieved, you can enter the next level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b26755751642910a150137c70a548d1.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=298 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b26755751642910a150137c70a548d1.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/0b26755751642910a150137c70a548d1.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f27f9d1d7b4c822bd410dd81f52bce6.poster.avif?t=1764856876\" width=298 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f27f9d1d7b4c822bd410dd81f52bce6.webm?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f27f9d1d7b4c822bd410dd81f52bce6.mp4?t=1764856876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397230/extras/3f9c73f65b5f8bf110b681ead9672a45.avif?t=1764856876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When petting a cat, there will be lovely graphic animations and sound feedback.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 12 different types of stores in the game, such as popsicle stores, dumpling stores, and jianbing guozi stores.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a total of 5 levels. After unlocking each level, new items can be obtained. Reasonable use of various items can increase the efficiency of petting cats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reasonably arrange props to let the cat store operate on its own.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple goals that can be accomplished without too much thought.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What <i>Kitten Food Alley</i> does <strong>not </strong>offer:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Customizable content.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Complex business strategy.</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Task goals with pressure or time limits.</span></p></li></ul>",
